history.title: Emotions Vocabulary
history.notes:
Elated – Extremely happy or joyful

Anxious – Worried or uneasy about something

Relieved – Feeling happy because something unpleasant is over

Frustrated – Feeling upset due to being unable to change something

history.title: Basic Greetings in French
history.notes:
Bonjour – Hello / Good morning

Bonsoir – Good evening

Merci – Thank you

S’il vous plaît – Please

Au revoir – Goodbye

history.title: Introducing Yourself
history.notes:
こんにちは (Konnichiwa) – Hello

はじめまして (Hajimemashite) – Nice to meet you

わたしのなまえは [Name] です (Watashi no namae wa [Name] desu) – My name is [Name]

よろしくおねがいします (Yoroshiku onegaishimasu) – Please treat me kindly

history.title: Wochentage (Days of the Week)
history.notes:
Montag – Monday

Dienstag – Tuesday

Mittwoch – Wednesday

Donnerstag – Thursday

Freitag – Friday

Samstag – Saturday

Sonntag – Sunday

history.title: Everyday Expressions
history.notes:
Ciao – Hello / Goodbye

Per favore – Please

Grazie – Thank you

Scusa – Excuse me

Buongiorno – Good morning
